\c 2
\s Ukulaywa kukaSolomoni nguDavida
\p
\v 1 Insuku zikaDavida zokuthi afe zasezisondela\x + Gen. 47.29.\x*, waselaya uSolomoni indodana yakhe esithi:
\v 2 \add Se\add*ngihamba indlela yomhlaba wonke\x + Josh. 23.14.\x*. Ngakho qina, ube yindoda\x + 1 Sam. 4.9.\x*,
\v 3 ugcine imfanelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukuhamba ngezindlela zayo, ukugcina izimiso zayo, imithetho yayo, lezahlulelo zayo, lobufakazi bayo, njengokubhaliweyo emlayweni kaMozisi, ukuze uphumelele kukho konke okwenzayo, laloba ngaphi lapho ophendukela khona\x + Dute. 29.9. 1 Lan. 22.12,13.\x*,
\v 4 ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* iqinise ilizwi layo eyalikhuluma mayelana lami\x + 2 Sam. 7.25.\x* isithi: Uba amadodana akho eqaphelisa indlela yawo\x + Hlab. 132.12.\x*, ukuhamba ngobuqotho phambi kwami ngenhliziyo yonke yawo langomphefumulo wonke wawo\x + 3.6. 2 Kho. 20.3.\x*, (isithi) kakuyikusweleka\f + \fk kakuyikusweleka: \fl Heb. \fq kakuyikuqunywa.\f* kuwe indoda esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaIsrayeli\x + 2 Sam. 7.12,13.\x*.
\v 5 Futhi-ke wena uyakwazi ukuthi uJowabi indodana kaZeruya wenzani kimi, ukuthi wenzani kuzinduna ezimbili zamabutho akoIsrayeli\x + 2 Sam. 2.32. 2 Sam. 18.5,12,14. 19.5-7.\x*, kuAbhineri indodana kaNeri\x + 2.32. 2 Sam. 3.27,39.\x*, lakuAmasa indodana kaJetheri, owababulala wachitha igazi lempi ekuthuleni, wafaka igazi lempi ebhantini lakhe elalisekhalweni lwakhe lemanyathelweni asenyaweni zakhe\x + 2 Sam. 20.10.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho yenza njengenhlakanipho yakho, ungayekeli ikhanda lakhe elilezimvu lehlele engcwabeni ngokuthula\x + 2.9.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa kumadodana kaBarizilayi umGileyadi wenze umusa\x + 2 Sam. 19.31,38.\x*, njalo kawabe phakathi kwabadla etafuleni lakho\x + 2 Sam. 19.28. 2 Sam. 9.7,10.\x*, ngoba ngokunjalo asondela kimi ekubalekeleni kwami ubuso bukaAbisalomu umfowenu\x + 2 Sam. 17.27.\x*.
\v 8 Futhi khangela, kukhona kuwe uShimeyi indodana kaGera umBhenjamini weBahurimi\x + 2 Sam. 16.5.\x*, owangithuka ngesethuko esibuhlungu mhla ngisiya eMahanayimi\x + 2 Sam. 17.24.\x*; kodwa wehla ukungihlangabeza eJordani\x + 2 Sam. 19.18.\x*, ngasengifunga kuye ngeN\nd kosi\nd* ngathi: Kangiyikukubulala ngenkemba\x + 2 Sam. 19.23.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho-ke ungamyekeli abe ngongelacala, ngoba ungumuntu ohlakaniphileyo, ngoba uyakwazi ozakwenza kuye\x + Eks. 20.7. Jobe 9.28.\x*, njalo uzakwehlisela ikhanda lakhe eliyimpunga lilegazi engcwabeni\x + Gen. 42.38. 44.31.\x*.
\s Ukufa kukaDavida
\p
\v 10 UDavida waselala laboyise\x + 1.21. Seb. 2.29. 13.36. 2 Sam. 7.12.\x*, wangcwatshelwa emzini kaDavida\x + 3.1. 9.24. 11.43. 2 Sam. 5.7.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo insuku uDavida abusa ngazo phezu kukaIsrayeli zaziyiminyaka engamatshumi amane; eHebroni wabusa iminyaka eyisikhombisa, leJerusalema wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lantathu\x + 2 Sam. 5.4,5. 1 Lan. 29.26,27.\x*.
\p
\v 12 USolomoni wasehlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaDavida uyise, lombuso wakhe waqiniswa kakhulu\x + 1 Lan. 29.23. 2 Lan. 1.1.\x*.
\s USolomoni uqinisa umbuso wakhe
\p
\v 13 UAdonija indodana kaHagithi wasesiza kuBathisheba unina kaSolomoni; wasesithi: Ukuza kwakho kuyikuthula yini? Wasesithi: Ukuthula\x + 1 Sam. 16.4.\x*.
\v 14 Wathi: Ngilelizwi kuwe. Wasesithi: Khuluma.
\v 15 Wasesithi: Wena uyakwazi ukuthi umbuso wawungowami, lokuthi uIsrayeli wonke babebeke ubuso babo kimi ukuthi ngizabusa; kodwa umbuso waphendulwa, waba ngowomfowethu\x + 1.5.\x*, ngoba waba ngowakhe uvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1 Lan. 22.9,10. 28.5-7.\x*.
\v 16 Khathesi-ke, ngicela isicelo esisodwa kuwe, ungafulathelisi ubuso bami. Wasesithi kuye: Khuluma.
\v 17 Wasesithi: Ake ukhulume loSolomoni inkosi (ngoba kayikufulathelisa ubuso bakho) ukuthi anginike uAbishagi\x + 1.3,4.\x* umShunami abe ngumka\add mi\x + Josh. 19.18.\x*\add*.
\v 18 UBathisheba wasesithi: Kulungile; mina ngizakukhulumela enkosini.
\p
\v 19 Ngakho uBathisheba wasesiya enkosini uSolomoni ukukhulumela uAdonija kuyo. Inkosi yasisukuma ukumhlangabeza, yakhothama kuye, yahlala esihlalweni sayo sobukhosi, yathi kubekelwe unina wenkosi isihlalo sobukhosi; wasehlala ngakwesokunene sayo\x + Hlab. 45.9.\x*.
\v 20 Wasesithi: Ngicela isicelo esisodwa esincinyane kuwe, ungafulathelisi ubuso bami. Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Cela, mama, ngoba kangiyikufulathelisa ubuso bakho.
\v 21 Wasesithi: UAbishagi umShunami kanikwe uAdonija umfowenu abe ngumka\add khe\x + 1.3,4.\x*\add*.
\v 22 Inkosi uSolomoni yasiphendula yathi kunina: Usumcelelelani uAdonija uAbishagi umShunami? Umcelele lombuso\x + 1.3,4.\x*, ngoba ungumfowethu omdala kulami\x + 1.6. 1 Lan. 3.2,5.\x*, yebo yena loAbhiyatha umpristi loJowabi indodana kaZeruya\x + 1.7.\x*.
\v 23 Inkosi uSolomoni yasifunga ngeN\nd kosi\nd* isithi: Kenze njalo uNkulunkulu kimi lokunjalo engezelele, uba uAdonija e\add nga\add*khuluma\add nga\add* lelilizwi emelene lempilo yakhe\x + Ruthe 1.17.\x*.
\v 24 Ngakho-ke, kuphila kukaJehova ongimisileyo wangibeka esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaDavida ubaba\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, wangenzela indlu njengokukhuluma kwakhe, isibili lamuhla uAdonija uzabulawa\x + 2 Sam. 7.11-13. 1 Lan. 22.10.\x*.
\v 25 Inkosi uSolomoni yasithuma ngesandla sikaBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada, owamsukelayo, wasesifa\x + 2 Sam. 8.18.\x*.
\p
\v 26 LakuAbhiyatha umpristi inkosi yathi: Yana eAnathothi emasimini akho\x + Josh. 21.18.\x*, ngoba ungumuntu wokufa; kodwa lamuhla kangiyikukubulala ngoba wawuthwala umtshokotsho weNkosi uJehova phambi kukaDavida ubaba\x + 1 Sam. 23.6. 2 Sam. 15.24,29.\x*, langoba wahlupheka kukho konke ubaba ahlupheka ngakho\x + 1 Sam. 22.20,23.\x*.
\v 27 Ngakho uSolomoni wamxotsha uAbhiyatha ekubeni ngumpristi weN\nd kosi\nd*, ukugcwalisa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma mayelana lendlu kaEli\x + 1 Sam. 2.31-35.\x* eShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Kwathi umbiko ufika kuJowabi, ngoba uJowabi wayephenduke walandela uAdonija\x + 1.7.\x* lanxa wayengaphendukanga walandela uAbisalomu\x + 2 Sam. 17.25. 18.2.\x*, uJowabi wabalekela ethenteni leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Lan. 16.39. 21.29. 2 Lan. 1.3.\x*, wabamba impondo zelathi\x + 1.50.\x*.
\v 29 Kwasekubikelwa inkosi uSolomoni ukuthi uJowabi usebalekele ethenteni leN\nd kosi\nd*, khangela-ke, \add use\add*celeni kwelathi. USolomoni wasethuma uBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada esithi: Hamba umsukele.
\v 30 Ngakho uBhenaya waya ethenteni leN\nd kosi\nd*, wathi kuye: Itsho njalo inkosi: Phuma! Kodwa wathi: Hatshi, kodwa ngizafela lapha. UBhenaya wasebuyisela ilizwi enkosini, esithi: Utsho njalo uJowabi, ungiphendule njalo.
\v 31 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Yenza njengokutsho kwakhe, umsukele, umngcwabe\x + Eks. 21.14.\x*; ukuze ususe kimi lendlini kababa igazi elingelacala uJowabi alichithayo\x + Nani 35.33. Dute. 19.13. 21.8,9.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* izabuyisela igazi lakhe ekhanda lakhe\x + 2.33. Hlu. 9.57. Hlu. 9.24.\x*, owasukela amadoda amabili ayelungile engcono kulaye, wawabulala ngenkemba, ubaba uDavida engazi\x + 2 Lan. 21.13.\x*: UAbhineri indodana kaNeri induna yebutho lakoIsrayeli\x + 2.5. 2 Sam. 3.27,39.\x*, loAmasa indodana kaJetheri induna yebutho lakoJuda\x + 2 Sam. 20.10.\x*.
\v 33 Ngakho igazi labo lizabuyela ekhanda likaJowabi lekhanda lenzalo yakhe kuze kube nininini; kodwa kuDavida lenzalweni yakhe, lendlini yakhe, lembusweni wakhe, kuzakuba lokuthula kuze kube nininini okuvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 2 Sam. 3.29.\x*.
\v 34 UBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada wasesenyuka, wamsukela wambulala\x + Hlu. 8.21.\x*; wasengcwatshelwa endlini yakhe enkangala\x + 1 Sam. 25.1.\x*.
\v 35 Inkosi yasibeka uBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada esikhundleni sakhe phezu kwebutho, loZadoki umpristi\x + 1 Lan. 29.22. Hez. 44.10,15. Nani 25.11,13. 1 Sam. 2.35. 1 Lan. 6.53. 24.3,6.\x* inkosi yambeka esikhundleni sikaAbhiyatha\x + 2.27.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Inkosi yasithuma yabiza uShimeyi\x + 2.8.\x*, yathi kuye: Zakhele indlu eJerusalema, uhlale khona, ungaphumi lapho uye ngaphi langaphi.
\v 37 Ngoba kuzakuthi mhla uphumayo, uchaphe isifula iKidroni\x + 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*, yazi lokwazi ukuthi uzakufa lokufa; igazi lakho lizakuba phezu kwekhanda lakho\x + 2 Sam. 1.16.\x*.
\v 38 UShimeyi wasesithi enkosini: Lelolizwi lihle; njengokutsho kwenkosi yami, inkosi, inceku yakho izakwenza njalo. UShimeyi wasehlala eJerusalema insuku ezinengi.
\v 39 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kweminyaka emithathu inceku ezimbili zikaShimeyi zabalekela kuAkishi indodana kaMahaka\x + 1 Sam. 27.2.\x* inkosi yeGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*. Basebebikela uShimeyi besithi: Khangela, inceku zakho ziseGathi.
\v 40 Wasesukuma uShimeyi, wabophela isihlalo kubabhemi wakhe, waya eGathi kuAkishi ukudinga inceku zakhe; uShimeyi wahamba waletha inceku zakhe zivela eGathi.
\v 41 Kwasekubikelwa uSolomoni ukuthi uShimeyi wayesukile eJerusalema waya eGathi, njalo wabuyela.
\v 42 Inkosi yasithuma yabiza uShimeyi yathi kuye: Kangikufungisanga yini ngeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngafakaza kuwe ngathi: Mhla uphumayo ukuya ngaphi langaphi yazi lokwazi ukuthi uzakufa lokufa? Wasusithi kimi: Lihle ilizwi \add e\add*ngilizwileyo.
\v 43 Pho, kungani ungasigcinanga isifungo seN\nd kosi\nd* lomlayo engakulaya ngawo?
\v 44 Inkosi yasisithi kuShimeyi: Wena uyazi bonke ububi inhliziyo yakho ebaziyo owabenza kuDavida ubaba\x + 2 Sam. 16.5.\x*; ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* izabuyisela ububi bakho phezu kwekhanda lakho\x + 1 Sam. 25.39.\x*.
\v 45 Kodwa inkosi uSolomoni ibusisiwe, lesihlalo sobukhosi sikaDavida sizaqiniswa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuze kube nininini\x + Zaga 25.5.\x*.
\v 46 Ngakho inkosi yalaya uBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada, owaphuma wamsukela waze wafa\x + Hlu. 8.21.\x*. Ngakho umbuso waqiniswa esandleni sikaSolomoni\x + 2.12. 2 Lan. 1.1.\x*.